<Base title="SocialProof for Electricians — Reviews That Win More Service Calls | SocialProof" description="Electricians: collect and display customer testimonials that make homeowners choose you over the competition. SocialProof takes 10 minutes to set up and keeps your calendar full.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Electricians
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Electrical work is high-stakes and high-trust. Homeowners are letting someone they've never met mess with the wiring behind their walls. The first thing they do is search for an electrician, scroll to the reviews, and look for any red flag. SocialProof helps you turn your happiest customers into the testimonials that close that search — before a competitor does.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The trust gap that costs electricians jobs</h2>
      <p>Most electricians are excellent at their craft but terrible at marketing it. Their website might be fine — but no visible testimonials means every visitor has to take a leap of faith. A competitor with 8 genuine reviews and yours with none? They get the call, even if you're better.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof closes that gap. Embed a testimonial widget on your website in 10 minutes and start turning every completed job into visible proof that you're the right choice.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What homeowners write when they trust their electrician</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Safety first:</strong> "Explained exactly what was wrong and why it was a hazard. Felt safe the whole time."</li>
        <li><strong>No mess, no drama:</strong> "Patched the drywall after running new wire. I didn't expect that — blown away."</li>
        <li><strong>Clear pricing:</strong> "Gave me a written quote before starting anything. Final bill matched exactly."</li>
        <li><strong>Problem diagnosis:</strong> "Found the tripping breaker two other electricians missed. Fixed in 45 minutes."</li>
        <li><strong>Timeliness:</strong> "Same-day appointment for a panel issue. Showed up on time, finished fast."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your electrical business</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your homepage or services page — 10 minutes, no web developer needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Send the collection link</strong> after each job via text — customers can submit in under a minute, no login required.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve testimonials</strong> from your dashboard before they go live on your site.</li>
        <li><strong>Your reputation builds automatically</strong> — new reviews appear live as they come in.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The right time to ask</h2>
      <p>Ask for a testimonial right when you collect payment — when the job is done, the lights are on, and the customer is relieved. A simple text: "Thanks for the business! If you're happy with the work, it'd mean a lot if you left a quick note here: [link]." That's it. Takes them 60 seconds. Builds your business for years.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every electrical service</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Panel upgrades and replacements</li>
        <li>Outlet and switch installation</li>
        <li>Ceiling fan and lighting installation</li>
        <li>EV charger installation</li>
        <li>Emergency electrical repair</li>
        <li>New construction and remodel wiring</li>
        <li>Generator installation</li>
        <li>Commercial electrical work</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free — no credit card required</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for one active widget with unlimited testimonial collection. Get set up before your next job and start building the proof that wins the one after that.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
